{"_id":"E0ED0JvP0lYbLc1E","name":"The Legacy - Team Move","permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Team Moves</p>\n<p>When you share a triumphant celebration with someone, tell them whether you see them as an equal. If you do, give them Influence over you and mark potential. If you don&rsquo;t, shift Superior up and any other Label down.</p>\n<p>When you share a vulnerability or weakness with someone, tell them a secret about your legacy (including your own true feelings about it) to clear a condition and give them Influence over you.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"team","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":""},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial success","value":""},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":""}},"playbook":"THE LEGACY","rollType":"","rollMod":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"VpqFj9wUwglqGKTc","name":"I know what I am","permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>I know what I am:</p>\n<p>Once per scene, when you defend a teammate you can shift Savior up and another Label down in addition to any other benefits from the move, even on a miss. If you do, add 1 Team to the pool.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"playbook","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":""},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial success","value":""},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":""}},"playbook":"THE LEGACY","rollType":"","rollMod":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"X3GCNWgvIrPFVPyY","name":"Symbol of authority:","permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Symbol of authority:</p>\n<p>When you give an NPC an order based on authority they recognize, roll + Savior.</p>\n<p>On a hit, they choose one:</p>\n<p>- do what you say</p>\n<p>- get out of your way</p>\n<p>- attack you at a disadvantage</p>\n<p>- freeze</p>\n<p>On a 10+, you also take +1 forward against them.</p>\n<p>On a miss, they do as they please and you take -1 forward against them.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"playbook","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>On a miss, they do as they please and you take -1 forward against them.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial success","value":"<p>On a hit, they choose one:</p>\n<p>- do what you say</p>\n<p>- get out of your way</p>\n<p>- attack you at a disadvantage</p>\n<p>- freeze</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>On a hit, they choose one:</p>\n<p>- do what you say</p>\n<p>- get out of your way</p>\n<p>- attack you at a disadvantage</p>\n<p>- freeze</p>\n<p>On a 10+, you also take +1 forward against them.</p>"}},"playbook":"THE LEGACY","rollType":"savior","rollMod":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"name":"Legacy","permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<h1>Legacy</h1>\n<p>Your legacy is an important part of Halcyon City.</p>\n<p>Name the different members of your legacy (at least two):</p>\n<p>____________________ is still active and prominent in the city.</p>\n<p>____________________ is retired and quite judgmental.</p>\n<p>____________________ is the next possible member of your legacy.</p>\n<p>____________________ is the greatest opponent your legacy ever faced...and is still at large.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Whenever time passes, roll + Savior to see how the members of your legacy feel or react to your most recent exploits. Before rolling, ask the other players to answer these questions about your performance. Take -1 to the roll for each &ldquo;no&rdquo; answer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>have you been upholding the traditions of your legacy?</li>\n<li>have you maintained the image of your legacy?</li>\n<li>have you made the other members of your legacy proud?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On a hit, one of them offers you meaningful encouragement, an opportunity, or an advantage.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, another is upset with your most recent actions, and will make their displeasure known.</p>\n<p>On a miss, something you did stirred up the hornet&rsquo;s nest&mdash;expect several members of your legacy to meddle with your life.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"playbook","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>On a miss, something you did stirred up the hornet&rsquo;s nest&mdash;expect several members of your legacy to meddle with your life.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial success","value":"<p>On a 7-9, another is upset with your most recent actions, and will make their displeasure known.</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>On a hit, one of them offers you meaningful encouragement, an opportunity, or an advantage.</p>"}},"playbook":"THE LEGACY","rollType":"prompt","rollMod":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ajxLH2HKsoL1yCUK"}
