{"_id":"rxJZVA8ZCJMM7ZkS","name":"Never give up, never surrender","permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Never give up, never surrender:</p>\n<p>When you take a powerful blow from someone with far greater power than you, use this move instead of the basic move. Roll + Savior.</p>\n<p>On a hit, you stand strong and choose one.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, mark a condition.</p>\n<p>- you get an opportunity or opening against your attacker</p>\n<p>- you rally from the hit, and it inspires the team; add 1 Team to the pool</p>\n<p>- you keep your attacker&rsquo;s attention</p>\n<p>On a miss, you go down hard but leave your opponent off balance and vulnerable.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"playbook","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>On a miss, you go down hard but leave your opponent off balance and vulnerable.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial success","value":"<p>On a hit, you stand strong and choose one.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, mark a condition.</p>\n<p>- you get an opportunity or opening against your attacker</p>\n<p>- you rally from the hit, and it inspires the team; add 1 Team to the pool</p>\n<p>- you keep your attacker&rsquo;s attention</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>On a hit, you stand strong and choose one.</p>\n<p>- you get an opportunity or opening against your attacker</p>\n<p>- you rally from the hit, and it inspires the team; add 1 Team to the pool</p>\n<p>- you keep your attacker&rsquo;s attention</p>"}},"playbook":"THE LEGACY","rollType":"savior","rollMod":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
